%N A393511 Number of partitions of n having five times as many even parts as odd.
%H A393511 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A393511/b393511.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%F A393511 G.f.: Sum_{k>=0} x^(11*k) / ( (Product_{j=1..k} (1-x^(2*j))) * (Product_{j=1..5*k} (1-x^(2*j))) ).
%e A393511 a(13) counts these 2 partitions: 422221, 322222.
%t A393511 CoefficientList[Expand@Sum[Normal@Series[x^(11 k)/(QPochhammer[x^2,x^2,k] QPochhammer[x^2,x^2,5 k]),{x,0,70}],{k,0,Floor[70/9]}],x] (* _Vincenzo Librandi_, Mar 04 2026 *)
%o A393511 (Magma) R<x> := PowerSeriesRing(Integers(), 71); [Coefficient(&+[x^(11*k)/ ((k eq 0 select 1 else &*[1 - x^(2*j) : j in [1..k]]) * (k eq 0 select 1 else &*[1 - x^(2*j) : j in [1..5*k]])) : k in [0..70 div 10]], n) : n in [0..70]]; // _Vincenzo Librandi_, Mar 04 2026
